    <b>New Business Report Option!</b>
    <ul>You can now add Business Registrations to your Business Comprehensive Report.&nbsp;&nbsp;These include Business Licenses, Fictitious Business Names, Tax Licenses and more.&nbsp;&nbsp;Simply check the Business Registrations checkbox on the Business Report selection screen to turn this option on.</ul>
    <b>New People Batching Options!</b>
    <ul>We have two additional options available for People Batching.&nbsp;&nbsp;When selecting the Output Single Best Address option, you may now choose to only receive updated phones and/or the addresses.&nbsp;&nbsp;To use this option, call the Accurint Batch Processing Department at 1-888-332-8244, option 2.</ul>
    <b>New Criminal Conviction States!</b>
    <ul>We have added two additional states to the Criminal Court Data.&nbsp;&nbsp;In addition to the seven states already online, you can search for criminal court data in Alaska and Wisconsin.&nbsp;&nbsp;More states are coming soon.<br><br>We have added two additional states to the Department of Corrections information.&nbsp;&nbsp;In addition to the 31 states already online, you can search for Department of Correction data in Michigan and Washington.&nbsp;&nbsp;Check the coverage icon to see what's available in each state and what's coming soon.</ul>
    <b>New Professional License States!</b>
    <ul>We have added Professional License Data in four more states.&nbsp;&nbsp;In addition to the nine states already online, you can search for professional licenses in Arkansas, Connecticut, Kansas and Ohio.&nbsp;&nbsp;More licenses in these and new states are on the way.</ul>
    <b>New Motor Vehicle State!</b>
    <ul>We have added an additional state to the Motor Vehicle Registrations.&nbsp;&nbsp;In addition to the nine states already online, you can search for vehicle registrations in Nebraska.</ul>
    <b>New Corporation Filing State!</b>
    <ul>We have added an additional state to the Corporation Filings search.&nbsp;&nbsp;In addition to the 39 states already online, you can search for corporate filings in Vermont.&nbsp;&nbsp;Be sure to check the coverage icon for the states to be added soon.</ul>
